{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845210/extras/maingif1080.gif?t=1724676996\" /><br>Gods love playing, and Hidden Tactics is their favorite board game. Play as a god of Humans, Elves, Orcs or Dwarves and defeat your opponent on a classic 7-round Hidden Tactics game. Master your strategy, and relax while watching a spectacle of fight &amp; glory.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Strategic Placement </h2>Place units and buildings on your side of the battlefield during the Preparation phase. You win a game of Hidden Tactics by destroying the opponent's villages, located at the end of each lane. Carefully manage your gold income and anticipate your enemy's next move by strategically placing your troops or using game-changing spells.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845210/extras/placingunit.gif?t=1724676996\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Enjoy the show </h2>Watch your units fight during the Battle phase! Don't worry about the fallen - they will rise again, fully healed, at the end of each round.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845210/extras/battlegif-optimize.gif?t=1724676996\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Build your deck </h2>Each faction has its specific units and buildings. Choose between 60+ cards to create the deck that best fits your playstyle !<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2845210/extras/creatingdeck.gif?t=1724676996\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Recruit Mercenaries </h2>As you can only bring a limited selection of units with you in battle, every deck will have its strengths and weaknesses. Some situations might require recruiting more powerful units : Mercenaries ! Each game features a random selection of mercenaries, with 20 mercenaries at launch. Be careful, as your opponent has access to the ex